I stole most of the code from Catalyst::Authentication::Credential::Facebook::OAuth2 by Florian Ragwitz, replaced the use of Net::Facebook::Oauth2 with Net::OAuth2, and added support to "grant_type" parameter.

These are to support both Facebook and mixi via OAuth2 in my current project.  Feel free to use it in wha

